  "units": [
    {
      "translated_text": "我们定期审查对员工的福利计划。在报告年度内，我们已",
      "unit_id": "733ff4741c456a0662664a8697cd1589f9dd03bfd5fda960e27a60c26e223e58"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "向符合条件的员工提供不同类型的带薪假期，包括但不限于以下",
      "unit_id": "ee00861679030df28c68fb9e6744ec992d4fdf555a0b0a16ef402fbd8febb1f3"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "，其中“生活幸福”假期（包括子女毕业假、子女婚礼",
      "unit_id": "b4532ec2e650d383eeb4d47066b83ac314d16a3eff2d8f37cf74fad370bf023a"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "带薪生日假",
      "unit_id": "70a614d455339485c76310f611fb056e84f4dd0d5ceee2059930ad1a16cea4fb"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "生日是人生的一个重要里程碑。因此，我们批准",
      "unit_id": "b76f5924f763310aa2b44db299f96ab6ca75b19af1c00d934e351b39ea3c91d0"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "带薪志愿者假",
      "unit_id": "aaa69a9a30d9b9716028630fb4858f4b42a9e24d6830521b404b0cd745f2a03e"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "我们深刻理解回馈社会的重要性。因此，我们",
      "unit_id": "e7d2ac1fc33ee01be1e7b3b27aaa049a8b33fc5cf3943ff111523569163cf2dc"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "鼓励员工积极参与社区服务，以",
      "unit_id": "3fedee407ae88d76a5923c83f65ae9135989c6959dbc794c57f438be357ae2f6"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "行动胜于言语。这就是为什么我们为员工提供带薪",
      "unit_id": "a7b1dcc25cf0a1022507619abd9b309bbcfa3ed130a46fa1a462e8ab26071efd"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "志愿者假，作为激励他们参与志愿工作的一种手段。",
      "unit_id": "d0fca4c2f7854d64e9c869825e1dce911ed564177e66ff26f305cab5ff2ab1af"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "5天全薪陪产假",
      "unit_id": "e88abb485f567b9e4c32c432e9c2ba3259c469421e6f27cf66522d1c01dee12b"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "自2013年3月起，我们已向所有",
      "unit_id": "6fab777c86f17c428188b178096269bc307c470723430f8432f9a0bdd8acfac4"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "符合条件的员工提供5天全薪陪产假。这优于法定的5天陪产假，后者",
      "unit_id": "086aed99d43a269e8c673d60a30744f29b0be46dddb3f3f9f63b14be12bd46af"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "婚假",
      "unit_id": "8190d8703296cd2d68990eb3e040bbe66b4832f2cd2cc2bace3086a040ee1dac"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "为了表达公司对员工近期结婚的支持，并允许",
      "unit_id": "fd39a901b0ceb62e137409f577e88530d46db8adfa3be3dede66be2575b163ac"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "他们完全专注于这一人生重要里程碑，享受新婚",
      "unit_id": "0769caf2b5da3af4128f5e3184af1b3eac7768cdb49ad652453ff8e38622ce7b"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "甜蜜。我们向所有符合条件的员工提供10天婚假。",
      "unit_id": "241d83d88ac364a3cdfeecb03da613145d469fdfb02ab7535c1ed8c9a2aa4b48"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "工龄假",
      "unit_id": "509502b857e7d11e99a84e2525159afefcacd689bfdaa30815b42ce2ba4f2659"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "感谢与公司共同成长的员工。我们",
      "unit_id": "ef1a60c32b7d05e86b50df44efe25885e5d5e4d04fc25fbd1ec8d529c53edab0"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "感激有员工一路相伴，让我们共同庆祝您的",
      "unit_id": "ccdde3301cd5065ef77a768cb825a0c872bb921531c1d088c830f87731f5f7d1"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "工龄。我们向在办公室",
      "unit_id": "ac9fc676a5ae4b7aab3074a01dc82817a494f4eb45991c443bf697815ff2d81d"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "工作满1年的员工提供1天工龄假。",
      "unit_id": "50e329fee13199485f82cbf995480b7aeda79f9c7f6108f5b663f471c3e0c6f5"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "考试假",
      "unit_id": "6ed99b859af5face8bbc28a16b0714b5fd70bc08a82c5e03882a28329f954436"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "鼓励员工不断追求继续教育，提升",
      "unit_id": "b3d8359d7aa383abe940f288c6528576d82b7c269724ab36f073f05131e3da9f"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "自身能力，以提高当前工作技能或为承担新",
      "unit_id": "cd96a49ea6b1029baf93d8ef9a4b4a0283156cfb484321116a91a2e14d1b6ec0"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "职责做准备。我们向所有符合条件的员工提供3天考试假。",
      "unit_id": "5d7ea509c4e1bee8ee0b2f682ef1f85457d0403648d8cd4279e8b2ffc4d267bf"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "“生活幸福”假期",
      "unit_id": "82452e96ac99439ea43f797a43129803a5fc00db13defe943132bab9ba340a61"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "营造家庭友好的工作环境，使同事能够在子女人生各个重要阶段分享",
      "unit_id": "19cc368d96d1d3625b79cac2271b75e9830f865ac6ff1bab7149f8e5a2e06bd0"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "快乐时刻。我们向所有符合条件的员工提供",
      "unit_id": "0db33767b7ad530b9a958144ce5d15f4caf07a55fb522cb821a9e329ffc172ba"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "4天假期。",
      "unit_id": "178d055d9db47131b62d9e88e53515390e2ef83b51a54b7f3c8a259b8bc4c8e8"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "2025年年度报告",
      "unit_id": "56b51d741cec09ea59621dcec4a7282efb36eca8b220dd9695260a480a14e481"
    }
  ]
